text: Josephine Gibbs (born 21 May 1938) is a British alpine skier. She competed in three events at the 1960 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1938 births Category:Living people Category:British female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Great Britain Category:Alpine skiers at the 1960 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Worcester, England
